<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>기보 정책자금 큐레이션</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #F7F7F5; color: #1A1A18; min-height: 100vh; }

  .header { background: #185FA5; color: white; padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem 1.25rem; }
  .header h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .header p { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.8; }

  .progress-wrap { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); height: 4px; margin-top: 1rem; border-radius: 2px; }
  .progress-bar { height: 4px; background: white; border-radius: 2px; transition: width 0.4s; width: 0%; }

  .content { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .step { display: none; }
  .step.active { display: block; }

  .step-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #A0A09C; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .step-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A18; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .step-sub { font-size: 13px; color: #6B6B67; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

  .options { display: grid; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .options.col2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .options.col3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }

  .opt { border: 1px solid #E2E0D8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 12px; cursor: pointer; background: white; transition: all 0.15s; text-align: left; }
  .opt:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
  .opt.selected { border: 2px solid #185FA5; background: #EEF5FC; }
  .opt-icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .opt-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A18; }
  .opt-desc { font-size: 11px; color: #A0A09C; margin-top: 2px; }

  .nav { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
  .btn { flex: 1; padding: 14px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; border: none; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
  .btn-prev { background: #E2E0D8; color: #6B6B67; }
  .btn-next { background: #185FA5; color: white; }
  .btn-next:hover { background: #0C447C; }

  /* 결과 */
  .result-card { background: white; border: 1px solid #E2E0D8; border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
  .result-card.top { border: 2px solid #185FA5; }
  .card-header { padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 0; }
  .card-top-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card-name { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A18; }
  .card-sub { font-size: 12px; color: #A0A09C; margin-top: 2px; }
  .badge { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .badge-blue { background: #EEF5FC; color: #185FA5; }
  .badge-green { background: #EAF3DE; color: #3B6D11; }
  .badge-amber { background: #FAEEDA; color: #854F0B; }

  .score-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .score-bg { flex: 1; height: 5px; background: #F0EEE8; border-radius: 3px; }
  .score-fill { height: 5px; background: #185FA5; border-radius: 3px; }
  .score-pct { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #185FA5; }

  .card-amount { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #185FA5; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: #6B6B67; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .tag { font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #E2E0D8; color: #6B6B67; }
  .card-meta { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; padding: 0 1.25rem 1rem; }
  .meta-box { background: #F7F7F5; border-radius: 10px; padding: 8px 10px; }
  .meta-label { font-size: 11px; color: #A0A09C; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .meta-val { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A18; }

  .toggle-btn { width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: #F7F7F5; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E2E0D8; color: #185FA5; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; }
  .toggle-icon { transition: transform 0.2s; display: inline-block; font-style: normal; }
  .toggle-icon.open { transform: rotate(180deg); }

  .detail { display: none; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-top: 1px solid #E2E0D8; background: #FAFAF8; }
  .detail.open { display: block; }
  .detail-section { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .detail-section:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .detail-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .detail-title.green { color: #3B6D11; }
  .detail-title.amber { color: #854F0B; }
  .detail-title.red { color: #A32D2D; }
  .detail-title.blue { color: #185FA5; }
  .detail-list { list-style: none; }
  .detail-list li { font-size: 13px; color: #1A1A18; padding: 5px 0 5px 16px; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E0D8; line-height: 1.5; }
  .detail-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .detail-list li::before { position: absolute; left: 2px; font-weight: 700; }
  .dot-green li::before { content: '·'; color: #3B6D11; }
  .dot-amber li::before { content: '·'; color: #854F0B; }
  .dot-red li::before { content: '✕'; color: #A32D2D; font-size: 10px; top: 7px; }
  .proc-step { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E0D8; }
  .proc-step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .proc-num { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; background: #185FA5; color: white; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .proc-text { font-size: 13px; color: #1A1A18; line-height: 1.5; padding-top: 2px; }

  .ai-box { background: white; border: 1px solid #E2E0D8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .ai-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #A0A09C; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .ai-text { font-size: 14px; color: #1A1A18; line-height: 1.7; }

  .hint { font-size: 12px; color: #A0A09C; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: center; }

  .restart-btn { width: 100%; padding: 14px; background: white; border: 1px solid #E2E0D8; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #185FA5; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 1rem; }

  .footer { text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; color: #A0A09C; font-size: 12px; }
  .footer a { color: #185FA5; text-decoration: none; }

  .loading { text-align: center; padding: 3rem 0; }
  .spinner { width: 36px; height: 36px; border: 3px solid #E2E0D8; border-top-color: #185FA5; border-radius: 50%; animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite; margin: 0 auto 16px; }
  @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
  .loading-text { font-size: 14px; color: #6B6B67; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <h1>기보 정책자금 큐레이션</h1>
  <p>기술보증기금 맞춤 보증 프로그램 추천</p>
  <div class="progress-wrap">
    <div class="progress-bar" id="prog"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content">

  <!-- Step 1 -->
  <div class="step active" id="s1">
    <p class="step-label">Step 1 / 5 — 기업 단계</p>
    <p class="step-title">현재 기업의 단계는?</p>
    <p class="step-sub">가장 가까운 것을 선택하세요</p>
    <div class="options col2">
      <button class="opt" data-step="1" data-val="예비창업" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">💡</div>
        <div class="opt-name">예비창업</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">사업자 미등록</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="1" data-val="초기창업" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🌱</div>
        <div class="opt-name">초기창업</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">창업 3년 미만</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="1" data-val="성장기" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">📈</div>
        <div class="opt-name">성장기</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">창업 3~7년</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="1" data-val="중견" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🏢</div>
        <div class="opt-name">안정/확장기</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">창업 7년 이상</div>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav">
      <button class="btn btn-next" onclick="next(1)">다음 →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 2 -->
  <div class="step" id="s2">
    <p class="step-label">Step 2 / 5 — 사업 분야</p>
    <p class="step-title">주요 사업 분야는?</p>
    <p class="step-sub">해당하는 분야를 모두 선택하세요</p>
    <div class="options col2">
      <button class="opt" data-step="2" data-val="AI/SW" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🤖</div>
        <div class="opt-name">AI / 소프트웨어</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">클라우드, 데이터</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="2" data-val="바이오" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🧬</div>
        <div class="opt-name">바이오/헬스케어</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">의료기기, 신약</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="2" data-val="제조" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">⚙️</div>
        <div class="opt-name">제조/하드웨어</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">스마트팩토리</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="2" data-val="그린" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🌿</div>
        <div class="opt-name">그린/에너지</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">친환경, ESG</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="2" data-val="IP" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">📜</div>
        <div class="opt-name">지식재산 (IP)</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">특허, 상표</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="2" data-val="기타" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🏪</div>
        <div class="opt-name">기타</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">서비스, 유통 등</div>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav">
      <button class="btn btn-prev" onclick="prev(2)">← 이전</button>
      <button class="btn btn-next" onclick="next(2)">다음 →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 3 -->
  <div class="step" id="s3">
    <p class="step-label">Step 3 / 5 — 기술/인증</p>
    <p class="step-title">보유 중인 기술/인증은?</p>
    <p class="step-sub">해당하는 것을 모두 선택하세요</p>
    <div class="options col2">
      <button class="opt" data-step="3" data-val="특허" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🏅</div>
        <div class="opt-name">특허 보유</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">출원/등록 포함</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="3" data-val="벤처" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🚀</div>
        <div class="opt-name">벤처기업 인증</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">예비벤처 포함</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="3" data-val="연구소" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🔬</div>
        <div class="opt-name">기업부설연구소</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">R&D 조직 보유</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="3" data-val="R&D과제" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">📋</div>
        <div class="opt-name">정부 R&D 과제</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">국책과제 수행</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="3" data-val="엔젤투자" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">👼</div>
        <div class="opt-name">엔젤투자 유치</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">3천만원 이상</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="3" data-val="없음" onclick="multi(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">⬜</div>
        <div class="opt-name">해당 없음</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">현재 미보유</div>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav">
      <button class="btn btn-prev" onclick="prev(3)">← 이전</button>
      <button class="btn btn-next" onclick="next(3)">다음 →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 4 -->
  <div class="step" id="s4">
    <p class="step-label">Step 4 / 5 — 자금 목적</p>
    <p class="step-title">어떤 자금이 필요하신가요?</p>
    <p class="step-sub">주된 목적을 선택하세요</p>
    <div class="options col2">
      <button class="opt" data-step="4" data-val="R&D개발" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🧪</div>
        <div class="opt-name">R&D 개발</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">기술 개발 자금</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="4" data-val="운전자금" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">💰</div>
        <div class="opt-name">운전자금</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">인건비, 임차료</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="4" data-val="시설자금" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🏭</div>
        <div class="opt-name">시설/장비</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">공장, 설비 구축</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="4" data-val="사업화" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🎯</div>
        <div class="opt-name">사업화/마케팅</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">제품 출시 및 판매</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="4" data-val="디지털전환" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">💻</div>
        <div class="opt-name">디지털 전환</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">AI/클라우드 도입</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="4" data-val="재기" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🔄</div>
        <div class="opt-name">재창업/재기</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">사업 실패 후 재도전</div>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav">
      <button class="btn btn-prev" onclick="prev(4)">← 이전</button>
      <button class="btn btn-next" onclick="next(4)">다음 →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 5 -->
  <div class="step" id="s5">
    <p class="step-label">Step 5 / 5 — 매출 규모</p>
    <p class="step-title">연간 매출 규모는?</p>
    <p class="step-sub">대략적인 규모를 선택하세요</p>
    <div class="options col2">
      <button class="opt" data-step="5" data-val="매출없음" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🌰</div>
        <div class="opt-name">매출 없음</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">개발/준비 단계</div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="5" data-val="5억미만" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🌿</div>
        <div class="opt-name">5억 미만</div>
        <div class="opt-desc"></div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="5" data-val="5~20억" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🌳</div>
        <div class="opt-name">5 ~ 20억</div>
        <div class="opt-desc"></div>
      </button>
      <button class="opt" data-step="5" data-val="20억이상" onclick="sel(this)">
        <div class="opt-icon">🌲</div>
        <div class="opt-name">20억 이상</div>
        <div class="opt-desc">BIRD 프로그램 가능</div>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav">
      <button class="btn btn-prev" onclick="prev(5)">← 이전</button>
      <button class="btn btn-next" onclick="analyze()">AI 분석 시작 →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Loading -->
  <div class="step" id="s-loading">
    <div class="loading">
      <div class="spinner"></div>
      <p class="loading-text" id="loading-msg">기보 정책자금 분석 중...</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Result -->
  <div class="step" id="s-result">
    <div class="ai-box" id="ai-summary"></div>
    <p class="hint">각 카드를 눌러 자격조건 상세 정보를 확인하세요</p>
    <div id="results-container"></div>
    <button class="restart-btn" onclick="restart()">← 처음으로 돌아가기</button>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
  기보 디지털지점 <a href="https://www.kibo.or.kr/dbranch" target="_blank">kibo.or.kr</a> · 대표전화 1544-1120
</div>

<script>
const A = { 1: null, 2: [], 3: [], 4: null, 5: null };

